{"title":"如何在Hexo文章中插入图片","slug":"如何在Hexo文章中插入图片","date":"2016-03-23T09:09:00.000Z","updated":"2019-12-20T12:03:53.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/如何在Hexo文章中插入图片.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"","covers":null,"content":"<p>如何插入的图片?<br>\n<a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/asset-folders.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://hexo.io/docs/asset-folders.html</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>编辑_config.yml</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"YAML\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">post_asset_folder:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<p>这样hexo会在每次使用hexo new title命令时在文章源文件目录下创建同名文件夹来存储资源.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>在markdown文章里如何引用?</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"DJANGO\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight django\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"xml\"></span><span class=\"template-tag\">&#123;% <span class=\"name\">asset_path</span> slug %&#125;</span><span class=\"xml\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"xml\"></span><span class=\"template-tag\">&#123;% <span class=\"name\">asset_img</span> slug [title] %&#125;</span><span class=\"xml\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"xml\"></span><span class=\"template-tag\">&#123;% <span class=\"name\">asset_link</span> slug [title] %&#125;</span><span class=\"xml\"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<p>举个栗子:<br>\n本篇文章名叫what-is-LDAP, 创建它时,会创建同名文件夹,把LDAP.png放在那个文件夹下.<br>\n引用时写</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"DJANGO\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight django\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"xml\"></span><span class=\"template-tag\">&#123;% <span class=\"name\">asset_img</span> LDAP.png DLAP organization %&#125;</span><span class=\"xml\"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<p><code>asset_img</code> 表示要引用图片, <code>LDAP.png</code>是文件名, 后面的是图片显示的标题，可含空格。 <code>asset_path</code>会直接将连接显示在页面中。 <code>asset_link</code>可以用作内部连接， 可以用于连接文件， 下载使用。</p>\n<p>然后执行hexo generate (或者hexo g)<br>\n就会将资源拷贝到和生成的文章相同的目录下,这样就可以了.在本地查看会显示不正常,但是部署到github上就显示正常了.</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"Others","slug":"Others","count":18,"path":"api/categories/Others.json"},{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Others/Hexo","count":4,"path":"api/categories/Others/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":5,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}]}